		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="282" y="+0" x="12" type="text"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">this is partly due to the fact that industry needs the wood and because growing populations need the land for agriculture</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
